機撒錢；錯過蘋果的股民，可能感覺錯過了整個宇宙，「錯過了騰訊，你是否感覺錯過了全世界？」"},{"pid":"99a21ec1b6f13c6a22ad52ab4886b098a6e67032","tid":1653063,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"大市升=qq 跌<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3c612dc2148ebb16840431079d4b428e6dc603","tid":1653063,"uid":202804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"做咩叫我??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf53e5acc6a23a168ddacf71f3b87006339d6d8e","tid":1653063,"uid":162674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"跌乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114de5d402667d7981fd07aaff068c227fc07225","tid":1653063,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"明眼人一睇就知大戶財報前㩒價"},{"pid":"903845493693d23388fd29dd3599351da37a703b","tid":1653063,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:04:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母跌乜撚野"},{"pid":"713b3f6cdcf71916ec0636761f7fd0fc662ba18d","tid":1653063,"uid":48835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"佢兩個仔6060 772係咁升"},{"pid":"cd2828562cd9a5bb8bdfbebbc88e258ebb3d65b0","tid":1653063,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">馬化騰老母俾狗屌！！！！！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4c021f3d1a7e69ef0a6f205884b6dcf92c6e9ec7","tid":1653063,"uid":3311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"垃圾騰"},{"pid":"ba14727a97aea84c736ff37f06c0b261a619d6dc","tid":1653063,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"b4c7853b35b5a92786245f02b5c7b5753f2e2949","tid":1653063,"